By BO Staff Writer This invitation was previously published on the BLF website. You are invited! Blacks in Dialogue (BiD), a series of Black First Land First (BLF) seminars, would like to extend an invitation to engage with its President, Andile Mngxitama, #FNB4 – the 4 black bankers dismissed by FNB, Patrick Matabeni and Tshepo Kgadima under the following details: Topic : “Lessons from the #FNB4 and the immediate need for a Black Bank!” Speakers: #FNB4, Patrick Matabeni and Tshepo Kgadima Respondent: Andile Mngxitama Date: 09 September 2017 (Saturday) Time: 6pm Venue: Devonshire Hotel, 16th Floor, Orient House, 49 Jorissen Street, Braamfontein Entry is free. RSVP to reserve your seat Yours in the Revolution Zanele Lwana Event Coordinator Contact details Gugu Zwane
